Execute any query:
   $rows = $wpdb->get_results($query);
Delete:
    $wpdb->delete( "table", array( 'id' => $id ) );

SELECT:
	global $wpdb;
        $rows = $wpdb->get_results( "SELECT * FROM table");

Notes:
File to be included:
    require( dirname(__FILE__) . '/../../../wp-load.php' );	
    global $wpdb;



